    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《呱呱归家记》是一款惬意而暖心的冒险游戏，运用简单的点击式操作，体验独特的拖拽难题机制。游戏任务是正确拼接便利贴，构建 Froggo 的世界。你可以按照自己的节奏完成拼图，享受一场毫无压力的温馨叙事之旅。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336240/extras/1f6bcc99c950a2fd25ffe98b344d5222.poster.avif?t=1772104384\" width=848 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336240/extras/1f6bcc99c950a2fd25ffe98b344d5222.webm?t=1772104384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336240/extras/1f6bcc99c950a2fd25ffe98b344d5222.mp4?t=1772104384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>回家参加蛙蛙狂欢节</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Froggo 只想回到家乡的池塘，与朋友 Buddy 一起庆祝春天的到来。但在回家路上，一群古怪有趣又难搞的角色拖住了他的脚步。也许他们也可以帮助他？他能按时赶回去庆祝节日吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336240/extras/b4220498ebfd6d7ff85873bdde98a4e2.poster.avif?t=1772104384\" width=832 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336240/extras/b4220498ebfd6d7ff85873bdde98a4e2.webm?t=1772104384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336240/extras/b4220498ebfd6d7ff85873bdde98a4e2.mp4?t=1772104384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>拼凑世界</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一关都有各式各样的手绘便利贴。你需要将它们正确拼接起来，为 Froggo 创建可以通过的道路，为其重建世界。<br>每解开一个难题都是一次豁然开朗。游戏机制简单易上手。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>轻松惬意</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸在可爱的 2D 手绘风格和氛围感配乐中，在暖心的世界里尽享轻松与惬意。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>友情与希望</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >裹上最舒适的毯子，泡一杯最爱的茶，来认识一下 Froggo 和他新遇见的古怪伙伴吧。与新伙伴交谈并互相帮助，齐心协力解决在途中遇到的一系列阻碍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游玩《呱呱归家记》，踏上一段充满希望的旅程，体验一个以归家、友情和羁绊为主题的感性故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336240/extras/07660ae27865595bea9531f0da06031d.poster.avif?t=1772104384\" width=802 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336240/extras/07660ae27865595bea9531f0da06031d.webm?t=1772104384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336240/extras/07660ae27865595bea9531f0da06031d.mp4?t=1772104384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>不着急，无压力</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >慢慢来，按照你的节奏完成拼图，帮助 Froggo 回家。途中会有一些可选择的经历，部分对话会使剧情产生微小变化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>放松身心的叙事游戏</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >逃离日常，让自己喘口气，游玩惬意的沉浸式拼图冒险游戏，这里不需要赶时间，尽可放松心情，舒适地踏上旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遇到困难时，Froggo 会陪伴你、鼓励你。快将《呱呱归家记》加入愿望单吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验触动人心的故事和幽默的对话。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用便利贴构建世界，为 Froggo 和伙伴们开辟正确的通路。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的 2D 手绘视觉风格。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >老少皆宜的故事，适合合家欢。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与 Froggo 一起遇见一群古怪有趣的伙伴，齐心协力克服阻碍。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最后，便利贴还可以这样有趣！只是记录无聊的待办事项可太没创意啦。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 个不同章节：1. 森林；2. 昆虫市；3. 田野与草地这里有许多可爱的插画便利贴，组成多达 18 个关卡。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >简单易上手的拖拽和点击控制操作。</p></li></ul>",
